ContentDesc_Abyssos - Sechster Kreis: Lahabrea insists that the only way to save the star from the horrors lurking within Pandæmonium is summary destruction. However, Themis and Erichthonios succeed in convincing the chief keyward to allow you a chance to prove the worth of another way. You are tasked with interring Hegemone, the keyward of Abyssos and a master of creation magicks in her own right. Succeed in this, and you may continue your journey into the facility's deeper circles. Fail, and Pandæmonium─along with its warders and creations─shall be reduced to nothing.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_34701_Text: Abyssos is my charge, and I shall not shirk my duty!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_34703_Text: Be swept away in a flood of aether!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_34705_Text: You cannot measure against a keyward!
